text: Gymnothorax niphostigmus, the snowflake-patched moray,Common names for Gymnothorax niphostigmus at www.fishbase.org. is a moray eel found in the northwest Pacific Ocean around Taiwan.Gymnothorax niphostigmus at www.fishbase.org.
